ata-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Walking is without a doubt the most important daily physical activity for senior citizens.&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;"><a href="https://www.hsph.harvard.edu/nutritionsource/walking/" class="" target="_blank">Regular walking can prevent or reduce cardiovascular diseases and diabetes, improve your sleep and mental health, and is an excellent low-impact weight loss method</a>.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">Ellipticals allow you to simulate walking from the comfort of your home.</span></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1670506638291" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1670506638291"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000">Ellipticals Provide Low-Impact Exercises</font></h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1670506641278" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1670506641278" style="display: block;"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>It’s not uncommon for senior citizens to have issues with their joints, hips, back, and similar.&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">Ellipticals provide a low-impact near full-body exercise, assuming you’re using the arm handles to engage your upper body - perfect for those with chronic pain.&nbsp;</span></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1672894966795" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1672894966795"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000">Ellipticals Are Easy to Use</font></h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1672894962569" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1672894962569" style="display: block;"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Elliptical machines do not require extensive workout knowledge to use.&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;">All you have to do is stand on them and start walking, and you’re working out.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;">This makes them very beginner-friendly and ideal for senior citizens.</span></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1672894967184" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1672894967184"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000">Ellipticals Are Great if You Don’t Get To Move a Lot</font></h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1672894961976" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1672894961976" style="display: block;"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Depending on their life circumstances, it can be difficult and exhausting for senior citizens to leave the house.&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">If you’re a senior citizen who doesn’t get out much for one reason or another, using ellipticals is a good alternative.</span></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675192974812" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1675192974812"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000">Ellipticals Can Fix Posture and Improve Balance</font></h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1675192972563" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1675192972563" style="display: block;"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Regularly going for walks or runs with your elliptical machine will help straighten your back, fix your posture, and improve your balance.&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;"><a href="https://journals.humankinetics.com/view/journals/japa/27/1/article-p34.xml?content=abstract" class="" target="_blank">A study published in the Human Kinetics Journal concluded that people over 60 years old who are physically active have a lower chance of falling than those who were less physically active</a>.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;">If you’re a senior citizen, this can have a massive impact on your quality of life.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;">Reports show that in the U.S. alone, <a href="https://www.cdc.gov/mmwr/volumes/69/wr/mm6927a5.htm" class="" target="_blank">36 million people aged 65 or higher suffer injuries from falling each year</a>.</span></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1673770422035" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1673770422035" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/70c2c924-03ef-4513-a44c-51d466c22296/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/Ellipticals-For-Seniors.jpg" alt="elliptical over 60 years old " class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" width="1200" height="800" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1200" natural-height="800"></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1670485569817" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1670485569817"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs gf-elm-left-lg" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">What to Look For in Ellipticals for Seniors?</h2></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1670506608137" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1670506608137"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000">Adjustability</font></h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1673764626941" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1673764626941" style="display: block;"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Adjustability settings such as incline level and exercise programs increase your workout possibilities.&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">The products rated the highest in adjustability usually have the most settings, but also are easier to set up for a senior person.</span></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1670485569822" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1670485569822"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000">Monitor Functionality</font></h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1670485569821" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1670485569821" style="display: block;"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>The more options the monitor has and the easier it is to read, the higher the grade will be.&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">For senior citizens, the monitor must be easy to see and intuitive.</span></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1672895064923" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1672895064923"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000">Portability</font></h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1672895061465" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1672895061465" style="display: block;"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Generally, the easier it is to move the machine, the higher the portability grade will be.&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">Compact and carryable devices will always win out in this category, but all of these ellipticals have some form of mobility, such as transportation wheels.</span></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1673764710691" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1673764710691"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000">Multifunctionality</font></h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1673764700638" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1673764700638" style="display: block;"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Ellipticals are fairly simple cardio machines with one main exercise method.&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">Having said that, some have additional multifunctionality by combining more machines into one.</span></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1673764716570" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1673764716570"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000">Price/Quality</font></h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1673764706800" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1673764706800" style="display: block;"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Price VS quality is judged relative to other products in the price range.&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; text-align: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px;">The premium choice on my lists is usually the highest quality, but other choices can have a high grade too if they outperform expectations relative to their price.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">Every choice on the list is a product I would recommend, and there are options for various budgets, so you can choose what’s best for your money.</span></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Image" data-key="image" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1670769562129" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-image" data-ver="1.0" data-id="1670769562129" data-resolution="3000x3000"><div class="elm gf-elm-center gf_elm-left-xs gf-elm-center-md gf-elm-center-sm gf-elm-center-xs gf-elm-center-lg" data-exc=""><img src="https://ucarecdn.com/011981d8-ffea-4a0a-b6af-d3de9b5eb2d9/-/format/auto/-/preview/3000x3000/-/quality/lighter/Ellipticals-machine-for-seniors.jpg" alt="best elliptical machine for seniors " class="gf_image" data-gemlang="en" width="1200" height="800" data-width="100%" data-height="auto" title="" natural-width="1200" natural-height="800"></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1670506766447" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="1" data-id="1670506766447"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h2 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2">How to Use Ellipticals for Seniors Right?</h2></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1670485569820" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1670485569820"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000">Consult Your Doctor</font></h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block" data-key="text-block" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1673764772057" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-textblock" data-ver="1" data-id="1673764772057" style="display: block;"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-left gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs gf_gs-text-paragraph-1" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><p>Before you start working out, it’s always a good idea to do a checkup with your doctor.&nbsp;<span style="color: inherit; font-family: inherit; font-size: inherit; letter-spacing: 0px; text-align: inherit;">It’s important to be in good physical health before exercising for all ages, but especially for senior citizens.&nbsp;</span></p><p></p><p></p></div></div><div data-label="Heading" data-key="heading" data-atomgroup="element" id="e-1670485569823" class="element-wrap" data-icon="gpicon-heading" data-ver="2" data-id="1670485569823"><div class="elm text-edit gf-elm-center gf-elm-left-md gf-elm-left-sm gf-elm-left-lg gf-elm-left-xs" data-gemlang="en" data-exc=""><h3 class="gf_gs-text-heading-2"><font color="#000000">Exercise Regularly</font></h3></div></div><div data-label="Text Block